cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a novel framework for applying convolutional neural networks to point clouds, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the extension and restriction operators, which are related to geometric representations (cs.GR) and the architecture of the network, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
